title: KMSpico v7 : Office 2013/2010 - Windows 8 Activator!
description:
So, as I was browsing the internet one day I came across this activator as I had been searching for hours looking for a new one since I was unable to get any of the other ones working properly. Everyone else seemed to have wanted me to take some survey to download this but luckily I found a direct download link and figured I would share it with the great community since they have done a lot for me making programs and such at hand at the ready. 

All it requires you to have is the latest Microsoft .NET Framework installed and once the application begins, it searches AUTOMATICALLY which version of Office or Windows you have that needs to be activated and once the search is complete just hit the activate button and you're done! That easy!

NOTE: Use KMSpico Installer folder for best results.

I just activated my Office 2013 Professional Plus edition and it works like a charm!
